NanoBBS - a light-weight and fast bulletin board software
=========================================================

About
-----
NanoBBS is a one-file, light-weight and fast bulletin board software, intended
as a proof-of-concept that a bulletin board software can be made this simple,
made of one single file, with only PHP as a requirement.
This software is released under the MIT license.

Installation
------------
Copy the file 'nanobbs.php' to your server, edit the $adminPasses and 
$modPasses variables to add administrators and/or moderators, perhaps edit the 
posting delay to your liking, and the page title. You're ready to go!

Notes
-----
This software is a proof-of-concept and NOT intended for production use.
